1293
01:12:38,630 --> 01:12:39,880
Leadoff, center fielder Lee Yong-min.

1294
01:12:40,090 --> 01:12:40,460
Here!

1295
01:12:40,710 --> 01:12:42,050
Batting second, left fielder Son Gwang-min.

1296
01:12:42,170 --> 01:12:42,510
Here!

1297
01:12:42,550 --> 01:12:43,840
Batting third, catcher Kim Jeong-ho.

1298
01:12:43,880 --> 01:12:44,010
Here!

1299
01:12:45,380 --> 01:12:46,720
Batting fourth, designated hitter Yoo Chang-soo.

1300
01:12:46,760 --> 01:12:47,260
Here!

1301
01:12:47,430 --> 01:12:48,800
Batting fifth, shortstop Choi Ha-seong.

1302
01:12:48,850 --> 01:12:49,180
Here!

1303
01:12:50,100 --> 01:12:51,760
Batting sixth, right fielder Lee Mun-ho.

1304
01:12:51,830 --> 01:12:52,260
Here!

1305
01:12:52,430 --> 01:12:53,850
Batting seventh, third baseman Kang Tae-sung.

1306
01:12:53,890 --> 01:12:54,270
Here!

1307
01:12:55,230 --> 01:12:56,640
Finally,

1308
01:12:58,980 --> 01:12:59,940
starting pitcher

1309
01:13:03,990 --> 01:13:04,530
Lee Woo-jin.
Yes!

1310
01:13:08,610 --> 01:13:08,950
Here!

1311
01:13:15,660 --> 01:13:16,330
Kongseo High School!

1312
01:13:17,290 --> 01:13:18,000
Let's go!

1313
01:13:19,000 --> 01:13:20,460
Woo-jin, it's been a while since you started.

1314
01:13:20,710 --> 01:13:21,250
Congratulations.
Thanks.

1315
01:13:22,090 --> 01:13:23,340
The pitcher decides the game.

1316
01:13:23,380 --> 01:13:23,960
Pitch well.
Don't worry.

1317
01:13:24,880 --> 01:13:26,800
I swear I won't give up a single run.

1318
01:13:26,970 --> 01:13:27,430
Hey!

1319
01:13:28,220 --> 01:13:29,260
Don't get cocky.

1320
01:13:30,180 --> 01:13:32,430
The pro scouts are here to see me.

1321
01:13:32,760 --> 01:13:33,930
Don't mess it up.

1322
01:13:34,680 --> 01:13:35,890
Don't worry.

1323
01:13:36,350 --> 01:13:38,520
Mess up my showcase and you're dead,

1324
01:13:38,980 --> 01:13:39,650
got it?
Well.

1325
01:13:40,940 --> 01:13:41,650
Mess it up...

1326
01:13:42,770 --> 01:13:44,320
I can't guarantee that.

1327
01:13:44,650 --> 01:13:44,780
What?
What?
Because

1328
01:13:45,780 --> 01:13:47,400
tomorrow is my showcase too.

1329
01:13:48,530 --> 01:13:49,820
That's not funny.

1330
01:14:02,630 --> 01:14:03,250
Since that day,

1331
01:14:03,840 --> 01:14:05,590
I've dreamed of this field.

1332
01:14:28,530 --> 01:14:29,070
This is a fastball.

1333
01:14:30,030 --> 01:14:31,160
This is a changeup.

1334
01:14:35,030 --> 01:14:35,990
Curveball,

1335
01:14:36,660 --> 01:14:37,410
like this.

1336
01:14:40,210 --> 01:14:41,250
This is a slider.

1337
01:14:42,880 --> 01:14:43,580
And one last one.

1338
01:14:47,420 --> 01:14:49,670
I've been training with you all along.

1339
01:14:55,350 --> 01:14:56,220
I'm ready

1340
01:14:57,220 --> 01:14:58,270
to pitch.

1341
01:15:04,360 --> 01:15:05,400
Are you all ready?

1342
01:15:06,020 --> 01:15:06,440
Ready!

1343
01:15:07,110 --> 01:15:07,610
Let's
advance to the quarterfinals!

1344
01:15:15,160 --> 01:15:15,910
I'm going

1345
01:15:16,330 --> 01:15:17,910
to write my own history.

1346
01:15:22,750 --> 01:15:23,620
Hello everyone,

1347
01:15:23,670 --> 01:15:24,920
I'm commentator Hong Seok-hyeon.

1348
01:15:25,210 --> 01:15:26,840
We're here at Dream Stadium

1349
01:15:26,880 --> 01:15:28,160
for the Round of 16 match of

1350
01:15:28,230 --> 01:15:29,220
the 2025 Haegi Cup

1351
01:15:29,380 --> 01:15:30,760
National High School Baseball Tournament.

1352
01:15:32,680 --> 01:15:33,380
Are you watching?

1353
01:15:35,430 --> 01:15:36,600
You better be watching me.

1354
01:15:37,260 --> 01:15:38,180
Are you ready?

1355
01:15:41,850 --> 01:15:42,980
Ready?

1356
01:15:43,350 --> 01:15:43,810
What...

1357
01:15:44,520 --> 01:15:45,270
What the hell?
What?

1358
01:15:46,130 --> 01:15:46,840
Wake up.

1359
01:15:47,310 --> 01:15:47,730
Oh.

1360
01:15:48,360 --> 01:15:48,900
I'm sorry.
You bastard!

1361
01:15:50,320 --> 01:15:51,070
You looked spaced out.

1362
01:15:51,780 --> 01:15:52,620
Ready?

1363
01:15:52,620 --> 01:15:53,790
Ready!

1364
01:15:56,280 --> 01:15:57,120
Pitch well.

1365
01:15:57,240 --> 01:15:58,660
I'll kill you if you mess up.

1366
01:15:59,290 --> 01:15:59,700
Yes, sir!

1367
01:16:06,250 --> 01:16:06,920
Play ball!

1368
01:16:16,430 --> 01:16:18,800
I can always feel you next to me.

1369
01:16:38,700 --> 01:16:39,530
Strike!

1370
01:16:42,580 --> 01:16:43,160
My dream once wavered,

1371
01:16:43,870 --> 01:16:45,410
but you caught my ball

1372
01:16:46,040 --> 01:16:47,250
and set it straight.

1373
01:17:03,020 --> 01:17:04,230
What are you listening to?

1374
01:17:04,680 --> 01:17:06,060
Share at least.

1375
01:17:06,100 --> 01:17:06,940
What the hell!

1376
01:17:07,310 --> 01:17:08,060
Ah.

1377
01:17:10,610 --> 01:17:11,440
Hmm...

1378
01:17:13,480 --> 01:17:14,360
Did you look at my playlist?

1379
01:17:14,650 --> 01:17:15,240
No way.

1380
01:17:15,280 --> 01:17:16,990
I never checked your phone.

1381
01:17:17,030 --> 01:17:18,320
We have the same taste.

1382
01:17:20,240 --> 01:17:20,870
What?

1383
01:17:21,370 --> 01:17:22,200
You like hip-hop?
I love hip-hop.

1384
01:17:23,790 --> 01:17:24,250
Nice.

1385
01:17:24,370 --> 01:17:25,660
Want to make an album together?

1386
01:17:26,080 --> 01:17:26,620
Album?
Yeah.

1387
01:17:29,170 --> 01:17:30,460
Then be my manager.

1388
01:17:30,540 --> 01:17:31,000
Are you crazy?
I was talking about baseball.

1389
01:17:32,210 --> 01:17:32,800
Then what?
Hey.

1390
01:17:33,550 --> 01:17:34,260
We should form a unit.
Form a unit.

1391
01:17:35,420 --> 01:17:35,920
A unit?
Yeah.

1392
01:17:36,810 --> 01:17:37,470
Let's go.

1393
01:17:39,140 --> 01:17:39,890
Sounds interesting.

1394
01:17:40,510 --> 01:17:41,300
You sure?
What do you think?

1395
01:17:42,220 --> 01:17:42,890
You'll do it, right?
Just follow me.

1396
01:17:43,810 --> 01:17:44,600
Wait!
